# 🧬 Melanoma Subtype Classifier

> Identification of molecular profiles specific to cutaneous melanoma subtypes through association rules on TCGA-SKCM multi-omic data.

**Author:** Manuel Rosario Marín Fernández  
**Masters degree:** MU Bioinformatics and Biostatistics · UOC / Universitat de Barcelona  
**Supervisor:** Romina Astrid Rebrij  
**Original thesis:** January 2023  

---

## 📋 Description

Multi-omic analysis of the **TCGA-SKCM** dataset (331 patients, cutaneous melanoma) applying the FP-Growth algorithm to extract association rules that identify clinical and molecular profiles by mutation subtype: **BRAF**, **RAS**, **NF1** and **Triple WT**.

The project has evolved from a static R Shiny visualization application into a **full web application** with a real-time executable pipeline, interactive rule visualization and integrated clinical documentation.

