## ⚙️ Pipeline

```
TCGA-SKCM data (331 patients)
    → Cleaning and normalization
    → One-hot encoding of 6 multi-omic variables
    → FP-Growth (mlxtend, min_support=0.015)
    → Association rules (min_confidence=0.85) → 317 rules
    → Filtering: lift>1 · leverage>0 · consequent=MUTATIONSUBTYPES
    → 11 clinical rules (Table 3, thesis document)
```

### Analysis variables

| Variable | Values | Description |
|---|---|---|
| `MUTATIONSUBTYPES` | BRAF · RAS · NF1 · Triple WT | Mutation subtype (target variable) |
| `UV-signature` | UV signature · not UV | UV exposure mutational signature |
| `RNASEQ-CLUSTER_CONSENHIER` | MITF-low · keratin · immune | Gene expression cluster (RNA-seq) |
| `MethTypes.201408` | normal-like · CpG island · hyper · hypo | CpG methylation type |
| `MIRCluster` | MIR.type.1–4 | MicroRNA expression cluster |
| `LYMPHOCYTE.SCORE` | 0.0 – 6.0 | Tumor infiltrating lymphocyte density (TIL) |

