## 🖥️ Web app features

| Step | Description |
|---|---|
| **1 · Data loading** | TFM data (Google Drive) · custom CSV · calibrated synthetic data |
| **2 · Preprocessing** | One-hot encoding · LYMPHOCYTE.SCORE as categorical 0.0–6.0 |
| **3–5 · Pipeline** | FP-Growth + rules + clinical filtering, configurable parameters |
| **6 · Results** | Scatter plot · TFM rules · computed rules · matches |
| **7 · Graph** | Interactive force-directed network · filters by lift and subtype |
| **8 · Documentation** | Clinical variables · statistical metrics · thesis context |

